		<DisplayName>Ocanni</DisplayName>
		<Backstory>Ocanni was formerly a great spirit-shaman among the Drota.  After the Stormlord rose to power, most other potential contenders for rule such as himself were hunted down and slain.  Ocanni managed to escape this fate due to a quirk of circumstance.  At the time of the Cataclysm, he had left his tribe to wander into the wilderness on a mystic vision quest.  He spent most of that chaotic time dormant inside a deep cavern whose walls were covered with ancient shamanic inscriptions of his people, his body sleeping while his mind travelled on astral journeys.  When he awoke, he found that he had somehow metamorphosed into spider-hybrid form.  Upon returning to his tribe, he found that his people had been captured and enslaved by the Stormlord's faction.

Since that day, he has split his time between wandering the wild lands and hunting down members of the Stormlord's tribe.  Now, however, he senses that changes are coming, and he wishes to pursue those changes and be a part of them.</Backstory>

